- Yorimitsu Hosaka (保坂 頼光) starts with "保" and ends with "光".
- The other characters that are not suspects are named after cardinal directions:
Officer Higashino (東野巡査) is named after "east" (東 ,higashi?) ;
Kokichi Minamide (南出 公吉) is named after "south" (南 ,minami?), while his nickname "nande" comes from the other reading of "south" in Japanese, "nan" ;
Kensaku Kitahara (北原 拳作) is named after "north" (北 ,kita?) ;
Mamoru Nishikawa (西川 守) is named after "west" (西 ,nishi?).
